~ start
???: [wave amp=25 freq=5]HAHAHAHAHAHA!!![/wave] Oh man, I can't believe you were stupid enough to walk right into that!
do get_tree().call_group("boss", "jump_in")
???: Aaaaaalright, we've been doing this song and dance for long enough bud. Let's just...
???: Wait, you're not the knight guy! What, are you lost or something?!
- ...
	???: You're seriously still reeling from that? It wasn't even that strong of an explosion, quit being a wuss.
	???: Besides, that's just the warm-up! If that's how you're gonna act before I actually start trying, that's just sad.
	???: Anyways, enough wasted time. Get up, let's get this over with.
	???: ...What do you mean, "Who are you?" Ugh, another new idiot. How many of you are there, anyways?!
	???: [shake rate=20 level=10]Fiiiiiine[/shake], I guess I'll do the speech without the whole group.
- What was that for?!
	???: What do you mean, "What was that for"? Buddy, [shake rate=20 level=10]you already know why I'm here[/shake].
	- Do I?
		???: [shake rate=20 level=10]D- "DO I"?!?!?![/shake] Do you think this is funny?!?! [shake rate=20 level=10]I'M HERE TO KILL YOU!!![/shake]
		???: Grrrrrr... Fine, you're probably new anyways. I'd remember someone who looked like they were trying to be edgy with linework like that.
		- What's wrong with it?!
			???: ...Buddy. What [shake rate=20 level=10]ISN'T[/shake] wrong with it? Terrible color palette, poor anatomy, it's derivative...I could do this all day.
			???: See, this is why we do this in the first place. You look like something a toddler scribbled, and I'm over here looking [wave amp=25 freq=5]Triple A.[/wave] Speaking of which...
		- And I'd remember how annoying you are. 
			???: You're just jealous case you look like a [wave amp=25 freq=5]fungus-infested pile of mucus.[/wave]
			???: Now shut up and let me do my speech.
	- I have no clue who you are.
		???: [wave amp=25 freq=5]Oooooooooh, that's why I dont recognize you.[/wave] You must be one of those bums who don't even get to wake up in the file dumps.
		???: That's a real damn shame. Cursed from conception and doomed to a meaningless life, and to top it all off you get plopped on some random island.
		???: Well today's your lucky day, Punk! Your suffering is gonna finally come to an end!
- (Unintelligible swearing)
	???: [wave amp=25 freq=5]Awwwwww, is somebowdy upset they feww fow such an obviows twap?~ Do youw need to wet some angew owt?~[/wave]
	???: Don't be such a baby. You knew the dangers of wandering around alone, and you still did it. It's almost like you want to die!
	???: Wait, are you...[wave amp=25 freq=5]ooooh, you're a new arrival![/wave] No wonder you fell for that; you're stupid, worthless, AND clueless!
	- What?!
		???: Hehehe, not my fault you're just so [shake rate=20 level=10]killable[/shake].
	- You talk too much.
		???: Oh, do I? Does having someone remind you how much of a [shake rate=20 level=10]mistake you are[/shake] get on your nerves? Keep crying. Noone cares about you.
	???: Anyways, you probably wanna know who's gonna be putting you down, huh?
???: Ok, where did I put the notecard Noble gave me? I swear it was...Riiiight, I put it in the inside pocket. Here we are...
???: [shake rate=20 level=10]Ahem.[/shake]
???: [wave amp=25 freq=5]Your miserable, incomplete existence will soon reach it's end, you pitiful creature!~ Your grotesque figure is no match for our perfect, hand-crafted bodies!~[/wave]
???: ...Or mine, at the very least. Man, this is way less fun without the entire gang here.
Fighter: Whatever, screw the speech. I'm the fighter of the group, and you'll address me by that name for the tiny amount of time you have left to live.
- ...
	Fighter: I know I made a huge deal over how meaningless you are, but if you have any basic decency...
	do MusicController.vol_reset()
	do MusicController.play_fight1_intro()
	Fighter: [wave amp=25 freq=5]Make this fun for me.~[/wave]
- You don't even have a name?
	Fighter: Why are you acting so surprised? [shake rate=20 level=10]You don't have one either.[/shake]
	Fighter: Now, as much as I'd love to keep chitchatting...
	do MusicController.vol_reset()
	do MusicController.play_fight1_intro()
	Fighter: [wave amp=25 freq=5]I have a new toy to play with.~[/wave]
do get_tree().call_group("boss", "start_fight")
do CutsceneManager.endcutscene()
